  "title": "Temporary Procurement Assistant (5 Months / East / Min Dip)  #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Temporary Procurement Assistant (5 Months) </strong><br /><strong>Contract Duration:</strong> Fixed-term until <strong>24 June 2026</strong><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, <strong>7:45am – 4:45pm</strong><br /><strong>Salary:</strong> <strong>S$2,500 (Fixed)</strong><br /><strong>Location:</strong>Tampines<br /><em>Occasional travel to Dover Campus may be required</em></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Support <strong>procurement tender activities</strong>, including:</p><ul><li><p>Scheduling project meetings during tender stages</p></li><li><p>Coordinating site show rounds</p></li><li><p>Managing tender clarifications</p></li><li><p>Supporting tender closing and preparation of management reports for approval</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Facilitate <strong>smooth information flow</strong> between internal teams and external stakeholders throughout the tender process</p></li><li><p>Build strong working relationships with College stakeholders to understand business needs and support purchasing solutions</p></li><li><p>Assist in resolving <strong>supply, quality, service, and invoicing issues</strong> between suppliers and internal teams</p></li><li><p>Guide requestors to ensure requirements and scopes of work are clearly defined before market sourcing</p></li><li><p>Prepare <strong>tender and procurement documentation</strong>, such as:</p><ul><li><p>Invitations to Tender</p></li><li><p>Letters of Award</p></li><li><p>Supplier compliance documentation in line with College policies</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Perform general administrative duties and any other tasks of similar responsibility as assigned by the line manager or College</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p><p></p>",
